      "span_text": "To estimate the QoL function in terms of time, Gaussian kernel-smoothing was applied.  Namely, for a particular time point t, the estimation of the mean QoL at this time point was the weighted average of QoL assessments, where the weights were determined by a parameter named bandwidth."
